a.n: World grand prix fight tna, final, tatneft arena, kazan, russia, 07.12.2018

p.d: The final of the "TATNEFT CUP" tournament 2018, which took place in Kazan (Russia), at the "Tatneft Arena" in Ice Sports Palace. Six events are scheduled for the event in three weight categories involving fighters from The Netherlands, Russia, Uzbekistan, Serbia, Greece, Romania, Turkey, Denmark and Spain.
